    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377420/extras/96d9614ab49961707c3c0c1dee164c99.avif?t=1749034019\" width=616 height=73 /></span>选择前进的道路，突破敌人的严防死守，踩着怪物们的尸体前进吧！在战斗中您不光可以使用拳击、踢腿等技能积攒连击数，还可以在合适的时机召唤强力武器，将敌人一扫而光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377420/extras/ec63a666cddc928d1cbad8a1ab658756.avif?t=1749034019\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377420/extras/7ff8f9c22e69c0de4820b74feeff617c.avif?t=1749034019\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377420/extras/31dd1de1a6cff835c106add72b6df686.avif?t=1749034019\" width=616 height=73 /></span><strong>2D动作类游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个无比经典的2D动作游戏中痛扁你的敌人，享受最纯粹的打击快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>积攒连击数吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以使用各种不同的攻击方式来积攒连击数，为之后的华丽连招积蓄力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>许多各具特色的关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在由不同类型的敌人组成的各种关卡中一展雄风，使出自己的真本领吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能力各异的敌人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人与敌人亦不相同！您需要躲避狡猾的敌人们使出的各种招式，找准时机给他们以迎头痛击！</p>",
